data.description: Wonderful, move-in ready 3 bedroom, 2 full bath, ranch style home is a must see! Outside, enjoy the private patio, new fence around the backyard & a newer storage shed. Inside, you'll find vaulted ceilings, freshly painted rooms, new light fixtures & ceiling fans, and refurbished hardwood floors in the entry, open family & dining room area, Florida room, hallway, and primary bedroom. There are beautiful new hardwood floors in the laundry room & kitchen, new carpeting in the 2nd & 3rd bedrooms, and new luxury plank flooring in the 2nd bathroom which also includes a new vanity. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances including many new items such as the microwave & garbage disposal, sink, faucet, and gorgeous quartz countertops, as well as refurbished cabinets that include all new hardware. The primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet and an ensuite with a separate soaking tub, walk-in shower, new double sink vanity, and new ceramic tile floor. The 2-car garage has a nice size attic for storage needs. The area includes walking paths, park district, shopping, and restaurants close by. Don't delay! Come and see this beautiful home today!
